sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Web as Web app
    participant API as API service
    participant DB as Postgres

    User->>+Web: submit order
    Web->>+API: POST /orders
    API->>+DB: INSERT order
    DB-->>-API: row id
    alt payment succeeds
        API->>+Web: 201 Created
        Web-->>-User: redirect /orders/123
    else payment fails
        API-->>Web: 402 Payment Required
        Web-->>User: show error
    end
    deactivate API

    par notify customer
        API-)User: email confirmation
    and notify warehouse
        API-)Web: webhook order.created
    end
